### Clinical Service API Collection
### Base URL: http://localhost:3002

### ─── SESSIONS ───

### Create a new clinical session
POST http://localhost:3002/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Name: Dr. Jenny Smith

{
  "patientId": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
  "sessionType": "opd",
  "chiefComplaint": "Persistent fever for 3 days"
}

###

### List sessions
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions?page=1&limit=20

###

### Get session by ID
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}

###

### Update session
PUT http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chiefComplaint": "Updated complaint",
  "diagnosis": "Suspected Typhoid"
}

###

### Complete session
PUT http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "diagnosis": "Typhoid Fever — Widal test positive",
  "discountPercent": 0
}

### ─── VITALS ───

### Record vitals
POST http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/vitals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bpm": 80,
  "temperature": 37.8,
  "bloodPressureSys": 120,
  "bloodPressureDia": 80,
  "spo2": 98,
  "weightKg": 68.5,
  "heightCm": 170
}

###

### Get vitals
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/vitals

###

### Get vitals history for patient
GET http://localhost:3002/patients/{{patientId}}/vitals-history

### ─── PRESCRIPTIONS ───

### Add prescriptions
POST http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/prescriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prescriptions": [
    {
      "type": "internal",
      "medicineName": "Paracetamol",
      "dosage": "500mg",
      "frequency": "Every 8 hours",
      "durationDays": 5,
      "instructions": "Take with water after meals"
    },
    {
      "type": "external",
      "medicineName": "Amoxicillin",
      "dosage": "500mg",
      "frequency": "Three times daily",
      "durationDays": 7,
      "pharmacyName": "Narammala Pharmacy"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get session prescriptions
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/prescriptions

###

### Get session prescriptions by type
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/prescriptions?type=internal

### ─── PHARMACY ───

### Get pharmacy queue
GET http://localhost:3002/pharmacy/queue

###

### Dispense prescription
PUT http://localhost:3002/pharmacy/{{rxId}}/dispense

### ─── LAB REQUESTS ───

### Request lab tests
POST http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/lab-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tests": [
    { "testId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001", "urgency": "routine" },
    { "testId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002", "urgency": "urgent" }
  ],
  "notes": "Patient has fever for 3 days — suspect typhoid"
}

###

### Get lab requests
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/lab-requests

### ─── PATIENT HISTORY ───

### Get patient clinical history
GET http://localhost:3002/patients/{{patientId}}/history?page=1&limit=20

### ─── IMAGES ───

### Upload image (multipart)
# Use Postman or cURL:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/images \
#   -F "image=@path/to/image.jpg" \
#   -F "caption=Left knee X-ray" \
#   -F "imageType=scan"

###

### Get session images
GET http://localhost:3002/sessions/{{sessionId}}/images
